---
title: Spiced Shrimp Burrito Bowls with Guacamole & Mango-Bell Pepper Relish
description: Get ready to relish this relish! Bell pepper and mango are sautéed with sugar until tender and jammy, then mixed with onion, lime juice, and olive oil for a tangy topper. The fruity garnish is perfectly paired with fluffy jasmine rice, Mexican-spiced pork, and creamy guacamole. Breezy burrito bowls with a tropical twist? Ahh… welcome to (weeknight) paradise.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/62a0b353e18e88006d07a7fc-d38dcf81.jpg
